## Login to MySQL using the root account before creating a new user
`mysql -u root -p` 
## Create a new user
`CREATE USER 'username'@'host' IDENTIFIED BY 'password';`
## Grant privileges
`GRANT ALL PRIVILEGES ON *.* to 'sammy'@'localhost' IDENTIFIED BY 'password';`
### If you want to remove the privileges
`FLUSH PRIVILEGES;'
